---
title: Sweet Chilli Pork Stir-Fry with Garlic Rice & Rainbow Veggies
description: Serve up a stir-fry loaded with all the good stuff! A colourful array of veggies and tender pork strips are tossed through a sweet and zesty Thai-style sauce for an easy dinner that packs a punch of flavour!

*Each week, we search the country to source the best ingredients, with a focus on quality and variety. This week's snow peas were in short supply, so we've replaced them with green beans. Don't worry, the recipe will be just as delicious!*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sweet-chilli-pork-stir-fry-44576bc9.jpg
